lines.text: Now get out and take that polecat with you.
Say, that's an insult to Petunia!
Nice job, Sheriff. That was almost worth the price of admission.
That's not the final round, Hudson.
Next time, you'll be in the ring.
You haven't got enough evidence to swing a jury.
I've got enough evidence for you to swing a rope.
You got any last requests before I put you out of your misery?
